 Music star Davido and his third babymama and ex fiancee, Chioma Rowland have seemingly reconciled. Recall that on March 31st that the lovebirds who many believed where back together had surprisingly unfollowed each other on the photo sharing apps. Fast forward to now, the couple seem to be back on, as at the time of reporting, Davido and Chioma have started following each other. This is good news for Chivido and Assurance lovers.